<div class="page-header">
  <h1>News help</h1>
</div>

<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span9">
    <p>The news system on BoarderLine allows boarding staff to post announcements that can be read by students. These announcements can be formatted using <%= link_to "Markdown", markdown_help_path %>. News posts are printer-friendly so a paper copy of any given announcement can be posted in the boarding house</p>

    <% if user_signed_in? && current_user.admin? %>
    <% else %>
      <div class="alert alert-info">
        You must be an admin to read the rest of this help article
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="span3">
    <p class="lead">
      Who can read news posts?<br>
      <span class="label permission">Anyone</span>
    </p>

    <p class="lead">
      Who can create news posts?<br>
      <span class="label label-warning permission">Staff</span>
    </p>

    <p class="lead">
      Who can edit and delete news posts?<br>
      <span class="label label-warning permission">Staff</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>